cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with power scheduling of Kalman filtering in wireless sensor networks, which involves topics related to control systems (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), mathematical analysis (cs.MA), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, since the focus is on control and estimation, cs.SY is the most likely category, followed by cs.NI, which deals with wireless networks. The other categories are also relevant but to a lesser extent.
